What Car? - August 2013  UK

252 Pages | True PDF | English | 80 MB 


What Car?  is a long-running UK monthly automobile magazine, for consumers rather than dedicated automobile enthusiasts.  It contains an extensive buyers' guide section to help consumers to buy the right car and provides tips on how to get discounts on cars and car accessories.
